- @nlp: So, what is our decision? Should we run our own candidate?

@nlp

- @run_cuno: Run Wilhelm Cuno of the <span style="color: var(--nlp-color);">**[+ nlp_name +]**</span>.
- @support_marx: Convince the <span style="color: #000000;">Center Party</span> to run Wilhelm Marx.
- @support_westarp: Support Kuno Westarp of the <span style="color: #3F7BC1;">**DNVP**</span>.





