@run_cuno
subtitle: This will cost us 1 resource.
choose-if: resources >= 1 and chancellor = "Cuno"
unavailable-subtitle: [? if resources < 1: Not enough resources. ?][? if chancellor != "Cuno": Wilhelm Cuno doesn't have needed support. ?]
on-arrival: nlp_campaign = 1; nlp_candidate = "Cuno"; industrialist_strength += 5;

WIP

- @endorsements_cuno: Scout out potential endorsements.

@endorsements_cuno

We can't win this election alone, we need support from other parties.

- @convince_spd: Convince the <span style="color: #E3000F;">**SPD**</span> to back Cuno.
- @convince_fvp: Convince the <span style="color: var(--fvp-color);">**[+ fvp_name +]**</span> to back Cuno.
- @convince_bb: Convince the <span style="color: #38C538;">**BB**</span> to back Cuno.
- @convince_bvp: Convince the <span style="color: #69A2BE;">**BVP**</span> to back Cuno.
- @convince_wp: Convince the <span style="color: #B8996F;">**WP**</span> to back Cuno.
- @convince_rlb: Convince the <span style="color: #52AE6F;">**RLB**</span> to back Cuno.
- @convince_dnvp: Convince the <span style="color: #3F7BC1;">**DNVP**</span> to back Cuno.
- @view_candidates: View party endorsements.
- @hope: We have concluded negotiations with other parties.





@support_marx
subtitle: We can convince the <span style="color: #000000;">Center Party</span> to run a compromise candidate.
on-arrival: z_candidate = "Marx"; nlp_candidate = "Marx"; bb_candidate = "Marx"; z_relation += 5;

WIP

- @endorsements_marx: Scout out potential endorsements.

@endorsements_marx

Marx can't win this election alone, he needs support from other parties.

- @convince_spd: Convince the <span style="color: #E3000F;">**SPD**</span> to back Marx.
- @convince_fvp: Convince the <span style="color: var(--fvp-color);">**[+ fvp_name +]**</span> to back Marx.
- @convince_bvp: Convince the <span style="color: #69A2BE;">**BVP**</span> to back Marx.
- @convince_wp: Convince the <span style="color: #B8996F;">**WP**</span> to back Marx.
- @convince_rlb: Convince the <span style="color: #52AE6F;">**RLB**</span> to back Marx.
- @convince_dnvp: Convince the <span style="color: #3F7BC1;">**DNVP**</span> to back Marx.
- @view_candidates: View party endorsements.
- @hope: We have concluded negotiations with other parties.



@convince_spd
unavailable-subtitle: The <span style="color: #E3000F;">**SPD**</span> is not interested.
choose-if: false

@convince_fvp
view-if: not fvp_candidate = nlp_candidate
on-arrival: fvp_campaign = 0; fvp_candidate = nlp_candidate;

We have convinced the <span style="color: var(--fvp-color);">**[+ fvp_name +]**</span> to support our candidate!

@convince_bb
view-if: not bb_candidate = nlp_candidate
on-arrival: bb_candidate = nlp_candidate;

We have convinced the <span style="color: #38C538;">**BB**</span> to support our candidate!

@convince_bvp
view-if: not bvp_candidate = nlp_candidate
on-arrival: bvp_candidate = nlp_candidate;

We have convinced the <span style="color: #69A2BE;">**BVP**</span> to support our candidate!

@convince_wp
view-if: not wp_candidate = nlp_candidate
on-arrival: wp_candidate = nlp_candidate;

We have convinced the <span style="color: #B8996F;">**WP**</span> to support our candidate!

@convince_rlb
view-if: not rlb_candidate = nlp_candidate
unavailable-subtitle: The <span style="color: #52AE6F;">**RLB**</span> is not interested in supporting our candidate as long as Westarp is running.
choose-if: not rlb_candidate = "Westarp"
on-arrival: rlb_candidate = nlp_candidate;

We have convinced the <span style="color: #52AE6F;">**RLB**</span> to support our candidate!

@convince_dnvp
view-if: not dnvp_candidate = nlp_candidate
on-arrival: dnvp_campaign = 0; dnvp_candidate = nlp_candidate; rlb_candidate = nlp_candidate if rlb_candidate = "Westarp"; wp_candidate = nlp_candidate if wp_candidate = "Westarp"; bvp_candidate = nlp_candidate if bvp_candidate = "Westarp";

We have convinced the <span style="color: #3F7BC1;">**DNVP**</span> to support our candidate!





@support_westarp
subtitle: We can support the <span style="color: #3F7BC1;">**DNVP**</span>'s candidate.
on-arrival: nlp_candidate = "Westarp"; dnvp_relation += 5; spd_relation -= 5; fvp_relation -= 5;

