@endorsements_westarp

Westarp can't win this election alone, he needs support from other parties.

- @convince_fvp_westarp: Convince the <span style="color: var(--fvp-color);">**[+ fvp_name +]**</span> to back Westarp.
- @convince_z_westarp: Convince the <span style="color: #000000;">Center Party</span> to back Westarp.
- @view_candidates: View party endorsements.
- @hope: We have concluded negotiations with other parties.

@convince_fvp_westarp
unavailable-subtitle: The <span style="color: var(--fvp-color);">**[+ fvp_name +]**</span> would never support him.
choose-if: false

@convince_z_westarp
unavailable-subtitle: The <span style="color: #000000;">Center Party</span> doesn't want to support him.
choose-if: false





@hope

Hopefully, our coalition is strong enough to win.

